metadata.name: White Rabbit Zero #1
metadata.description: Christmas, 2063. A tale from the Metaverse 1.0 era is still being circulated in all corners of cyber dimensions, especially during this special time of the year. Once upon a time, when the White Rabbit was hopping between wonderlands and matrixes, he came across the Christmas algorithm and met Santa. They chatted and exchanged ideas. With curiosity and kindness in their hearts, they joined hands and decided that this year, they will bring joy to the world. White Rabbit NFT is your utility & access token to all perks and benefits of the GATE ecosystem, including whitelist access, discounted presale, staking rewards, airdrops, partner perks, private channels, and more!
